--------------------------------DESCRIPTION---------------------------------
Optizelle is an opten source software library designed to solve general purpose
nonlinear optimizations problems.


----------------------------INSTALLATION AND USE----------------------------
Please see the Optizelle documentation online at

                http://www.optimojoe.com/optizelle

for detailed instructions on the installation and use of Optizelle.  For 
advanced users, installation may be as simple as

    mkdir build
    cd build
    ccmake ../src
    make
    make install
